body:
Comment 8: 
Regarding the "dwarfdump ERROR:  dwarf_srclines:  DW_DLE_LINE_NUM_OPERANDS_BAD (56)"
message, given that it also shows up in 1.2, it seems unlikely to be what is causing the
bad gdb behavior. That said, it seems worth fixing, and maybe after fixing it, there'd
be another, new, more helpful error.

Based on our private communication, I am going to assume that you are looking into this
until I hear otherwise. Let me know how I can help!
